            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "XM5K2",
              "name": "Tags",
              "fill": "$foreground-secondary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Roblox • Typescript • Blender • Solid.js",
              "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
              "fontSize": 11,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            },
            {
              "type": "rectangle",
              "id": "afZDU",
              "name": "Divider Line",
              "fill": "$border-subtle",
              "width": 342,
              "height": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "FjvkW",
              "name": "Content Body",
              "width": 342,
              "layout": "vertical",
              "gap": 16,
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "x6E7UN",
                  "name": "Paragraph 1",
                  "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "When my kids asked me to make a game with them, I knew I was in trouble. They're Roblox fanatics, and I'd never touched the platform. But after some initial tinkering with the editor, I discovered something that changed everything: a thriving community building Roblox games using TypeScript and React. Suddenly, I was all in.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "psvdU",
                  "name": "Paragraph 2",
                  "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "I wanted to create something where the gameplay emerged naturally from physics, so marble racing seemed like the perfect fit. You know—place your bets, watch chaos unfold. But then I thought: what if you were the marble? And what if you could drive it?",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "H7ASO",
                  "name": "Paragraph 3",
                  "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "The learning curve hit me like a truck. Roblox is multiplayer by default, which means constant client-server communication and a whole new way of thinking about game architecture. I spent weeks wrapping my head around remote events, data stores, and keeping everything in sync across players.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "AMxKw",
                  "name": "Paragraph 4",
                  "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "The current beta features just the first two areas, but I've built the foundation to expand significantly from here. If you've got a Roblox fan in your life (or are one yourself), I'd love for you to check it out and share your feedback.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                },
                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "id": "o7zaR",
                  "name": "Paragraph 5",
                  "fill": "$foreground-primary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Sometimes the best projects are the ones your kids rope you into.",
                  "lineHeight": 1.5,
                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                  "fontSize": 14,
                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                }
